This paper is primarily focused on face-related tasks and the use of transfer learning to improve performance. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms and the analysis of filters, which suggests that it could also fit into categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of large datasets, which could place it in the cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of compression techniques, which could place it in the cs.MM (Multimedia) category.
